# ============================================================================
# Patch Explanation: test_dataloader.py
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Purpose:
#    - Enable DataLoader tests to run on NPU devices
#    - Ensure tensor creation and operations use NPU device
#    - Add NPU-specific test cases and skip conditions
#
# 2. Key Modifications:
#    a) Import torch_npu module and transfer_to_npu utility
#    b) Add .npu() calls to tensor creation for TensorDataset tests
#    c) Add _move_dataset_to_npu() helper method for DataLoader tests
#    d) Add NPU IPC skip condition for multiprocessing contexts
#    e) Add default_collate NPU device test
#
# 3. Modification Patterns:
#    - TensorDataset tests: Convert all torch.randn/rand calls to .npu()
#      Example: torch.randn(15, 10) -> torch.randn(15, 10).npu()
#    - StackDataset tests: Add .npu() to all TensorDataset instances
#    - ConcatDataset tests: Add .npu() to tensor creation
#    - DataLoader tests: Use helper method to move dataset to NPU
#
# 4. NPU IPC Requirement:
#    - NPU IPC tensor sharing requires PYTORCH_NPU_ALLOC_CONF expandable_segments:True
#    - Added skip condition to prevent test failures on NPU without this config
#
# 5. Test Coverage:
#    - TensorDataset: test_len, test_getitem, test_getitem_1d, test_single_tensor, test_many_tensors
#    - StackDataset: test_mixed, test_size_mismatch, test_len, test_single, test_getitem, test_getitems variants
#    - ConcatDataset: test_add_dataset, test_iterable_dataset_err
#    - DataLoader: test_sequential_nonbatch, test_sequential_batch, test_multiprocessing_contexts
#    - DistributedSampler: test_distributed_sampler_invalid_rank, sampler tests
#
# 6. Key Changes Summary:
#    - 245 lines of changes across test classes
#    - ~50+ tensor creations converted to NPU device
#    - 1 helper method added (_move_dataset_to_npu)
#    - 1 skip decorator added (NPU IPC requirement)
#    - 1 new test case added (default_collate NPU test)
#
